John Glenn High School
January 30, 2019 at 8:48 AM Â·

Freshmen Orientation Night will be on Monday, Feb. 4, 2019 (alternate date for inclement weather will be Feb. 7, 2019) at the John Glenn High School auditorium. Locker selection will start at 6:00 p.m. (a parent
must attend for locker selection) and the meeting in the auditorium will start
promptly at 6:25 p.m. A short cookie and punch reception will follow in the FACS room. We look forward to meeting new parents and students at this informative evening.

JGHS counselors and principals will provide an overview of the changes in the graduation requirements for the Class of 2023 including new Graduation Pathway information. We welcome any questions after the presentation. Please plan to attend! Online course selections will be completed the week of February 11 with UMS staff.

Please plan to attend! See you there!
